04, 7,894,052 stock options remain available for grant under the Employee Plans and 117,800", "bbox": [162.5, 566.8, 1139.3, 589.9]}, {"text": "stock options remain available for grant under the Director Plan.", "bbox": [125.0, 590.7, 653.5, 613.8]}, {"text": "The Employee Plans primarily provide for the grant of options (both non-qualified options and incentive stock options", "bbox": [162.5, 638.7, 1139.5, 661.8]}, {"text": "as defined in each respective plan), stock appreciation rights and restricted stock to key employees of the Company or its", "bbox": [125.0, 662.6, 1139.3, 685.7]}, {"text": "subsidiaries (as determined by the Compensation Committee of the Board of Directors) for periods not exceeding ten years.", "bbox": [125.0, 686.6, 1144.5, 709.7]}, {"text": "Options granted under the Employee Plans vest incrementally in periods ranging from six months to four years.  Under the", "bbox": [125.0, 710.6, 1139.4, 733.7]}, {"text": "Director Plan, nonemployee directors are entitled to an annual distribution of 1,800 shares of common stock and options to", "bbox": [125.0, 734.5, 1139.4, 757.6]}, {"text": "purchase an additional 8,000 shares.  All options granted under the Director Plan are non-qualified, vest immediately and", "bbox": [125.0, 758.5, 1139.3, 781.6]}, {"text": "are exercisable on the date of grant.  Options granted under the Director Plan are exercisable for ten years from the grant", "bbox": [125.0, 782.5, 1139.3, 805.6]}, {"text": "date.", "bbox": [125.0, 806.4, 169.0, 829.5]}, {"text": "A summary of the status of the Company’s stock options for the years ended December 31, 2004, 2003 and 2002 is", "bbox": [162.5, 854.4, 1139.3, 877.5]}, {"text": "presented below (000’s omitted except per share data):", "bbox": [125.0, 878.3, 575.3, 901.4]}, {"text": "2004", "bbox": [467.1, 914.6, 513.2, 937.7]}, {"text": "2003", "bbox": [692.1, 914.6, 738.2, 937.7]}, {"text": "2002", "bbox": [917.1, 914.6, 963.2, 937.7]}, {"text": "Weighted-", "bbox": [479.6, 